      p(style="font-size:20px; line-height: 150%;")
        | After college, I decided to venture away from my native Chicago and taught math at a high school in Oakland as part of the Teach for America program. After TFA, I worked on a machine learning project with an agricultural robotics startup in Mountain View. 
      p(style="font-size:20px; line-height: 150%;")
        | PMs at Facebook come from a variety of disciplines, places, and world views. My favorite part of being an RPM is getting to see this diversity in action when people think out loud during brainstorm sessions- there's so much creativity and passion! 
