  section#four.main.style2.right.dark.fullscreen
    .content.box.interviewPage
      header
        h2(style="font-size:40px") Zuck Reviews in Spandex? 
        h2(style="font-size: 40px") You betcha. 
      p(style="font-size:20px; line-height: 150%;")
        | Fun fact: the first product review I did with Mark Zuckerberg (on week 7 of being at the company) I had to do in spandex bike shorts because I had lost a bet the day before against an RPM Manager. The review went well though!
      p(style="font-size:20px; line-height: 150%;")
        | Jokes aside, I come from a more traditional computer science background. I grew up and studied in Canada but decided to make the move out to Silicon Valley after a few great internship experiences. For one of my rotations, I got to completely reimagine Facebook Pages on mobile. As a PM, I've learned how to feel when a team is happy, operating well, and working towards a vision that everyone is bought into.
